{"tid":1569042,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"到今時今日仲有手足用緊支動 支銀?","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T13:18:48.000Z","uid":36134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"54696d5b8df80db2123ac0dc0101009b45fcd72c","tid":1569042,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:58:26.000Z","msg":"真係令我好撚嬲<br />\n你地會唔會感到慚愧？<br />\n對唔對得住死左十幾位手足？<br />\n對唔對得住被捕既千幾位手足<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好再猶豫<br />\n仲有幾耐都好 要賠錢都好<br />\n都要cut<br />\n<br />\n唔好再猶豫<br />\n果斷剪"},{"pid":"d207863b07653ef4daa668149e71374409fc48ca","tid":1569042,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c7275a3fbbdbb98c19451da3eae07697585df64","tid":1569042,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"【終極核彈】《願榮光》之後－成立海外臨時民主政府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566796\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566796</a><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光》之後。。。<br />\n天滅中共 平反六四！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freehongkonghkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehongkonghkg&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=7d578aaa\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"5d1b991a04b1cf8536177c4d56718c883793dd9f","tid":1569042,"uid":319971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:59:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c45530d67872bb8bf82fcfe67ef4f3b7ac8229","tid":1569042,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f37d7880d9b29f7cb18988e5c3a1727a6cdaa308","tid":1569042,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:00:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3021e514385587ce7efd000844435df2ac7b80d7","tid":1569042,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f2c928403ba49ff85ee8bf9c681210c6c204c2e","tid":1569042,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"幾日前發現自動續約左 依家cut緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b172d49b35f082ea0ace73abcb9f4ada253e9978","tid":1569042,"uid":114351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:03:03.000Z","msg":"915。聽日見！<br />\n721 831！<br />\n銅鑼灣等！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pXRpzzD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpXRpzzD.jpg&h=eb0be5ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vv3GBNZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvv3GBNZ.jpg&h=893fe7ec&s={SIZE}\" />"